entries.journal_entry_description: You now have permission to enter the Etyyy region of Kashyyyk, also known as the Hunting Grounds.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Enter Etyyy, the Hunting Grounds, and speak with Sordaan Xris.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Sordaan has refused to speak with you. Seek Ziven Tissak in the Rodian camp instead.
